org.fhnw.aigs.commons

Class LogRouter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.LogRouter

  • public class LogRouter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is to route the logging of the AIGS Commons project
    If an instance of AIGS Commons is running on the AIGS server, all log messages will be suppressed to relieve the server-side logging system.
    Otherwise, a standard logger will be used
    Version:
    v1.0
    Author:
    Raphael Stoeckli (26.02.2015)
